{"tid":1530206,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(文宣/IT請入) 不如為今次運動建立一個資料庫","createTime":"2019-09-02T01:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T11:29:00.000Z","uid":155292,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"221d591c9584adcf56057bf1394b3b8cb4882059","tid":1530206,"uid":155292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:43:49.000Z","msg":"接近三個月以來太多事發生<br />\n資訊太多太亂<br />\n<br />\n好多時就咁一兩張相傳出嚟，<br />\n已經搞唔清楚係邊度、幾時嘅事<br />\n<br />\n可能亦都係咁樣間接導致BBC炒車事件(POPO汽油彈改圖)發生？<br />\n<br />\n不如整個好似Wikipedia咁嘅小型資料庫<br />\n按每一日嘅重大事件去分類<br />\n裏面除咗有手足影嘅相、片 (仲要有埋擁有人tg，方便外媒搵片主)，亦都可以link返相關嘅外媒報道<br />\n<br />\n等關注事件嘅人可以好容易睇到一啲可信嘅資料<br />\n(之前見過有人send個list出嚟係警暴事件，可以base on個list每一件事都可以再㩒入去睇詳細嘅描述同埋相片)<br />\n<br />\n在申請翻個吸睛嘅URL<br />\n例如<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkpoliceviolence.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkpoliceviolence.com&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FWLTbr5529Gqcy%2B2MeRGono%3D&h=60739e6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hkpoliceviolence.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://hongkongsos.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhongkongsos.com&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FWLTbr5529Gqcy%2B2MeRGono%3D&h=e42fe456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hongkongsos.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://hongkonghumanitariancrisis.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhongkonghumanitariancrisis.com&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FWLTbr5529Gqcy%2B2MeRGono%3D&h=3b4ed613\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hongkonghumanitariancrisis.com</a><br />\n<br />\n我唔識IT、亦都唔識整圖<br />\n只係識少少英文，如果有需要可以做翻譯工作<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇？"},{"pid":"d47b5b45c67ee14b1668cd88a99509f0914e3e8a","tid":1530206,"uid":274393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:45:48.000Z","msg":"好提議。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efc1ad9b323a29ed7f2638f0bdb209d0671c579","tid":1530206,"uid":300514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:57:38.000Z","msg":"有手足整咗英文t